column1: Traffic reports will resume Friday September 27 at 4:00 p.m.

column4: The roadway is shut down in both directions between Alumni Dr and Cooper Dr due to downed wires.  KU has been notified.
Motorists should treat intersections with dark traffic signals as 4-way stops.
Effective September 27 at 10 a.m. to September 27 at 8 p.m.
